Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H816CF0&\3c&HC5C5F5&\fs+0\be1\bord1.8}啊 兩人共享喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自斷其翼的決意已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下還能行動更讓人驚異
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們失去了要由天使進行救助的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-1}(服從我去保護大門的鑰之守人\N如今聽命，解除堅守大門的鎖之番人之任務!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(高速咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解凍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 小瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希兒德大人 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你來說明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個奇怪的機器人強迫跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再被小丫頭綁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後被吉祥物壓住不能動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全正確
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有句格言非常適合現在這場景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這完全不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子格言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有非常充分奪取卵的機會喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要按計劃讓詩寇蒂呼喚出天使再奪取過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做天使和使魔就不能交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓全員都成為使魔的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為絕對不會被反擊的最強戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫欲擒故縱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐被使魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏被發現的話就失去救援的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明丟下姐姐逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也反省一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就反省過很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是你想看到我難過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣做毫無任何作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省早就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只是按選擇來進行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說麼 當然是全力救出大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是最好的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這樣說 也該有計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你那麼大聲的笨字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你想得那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解的話就別去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼輕易答應下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是輕易答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在蓓兒丹蒂陷入危機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我什麼都做不了那還留著何用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒聽說過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 螢一的話能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有螢一才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 螢一 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬就了結的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好支撐住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體裏可能會有失落感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是可能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起來也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德 詩寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逃跑麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂 現在是呼喚的時機了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求召喚天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想救出蓓兒丹蒂 兀兒德和佩歐斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有你能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和天使共同生活的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑現在的你是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 並不是去羨慕誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是真心想要見天使的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我力量 戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了 高貴真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 被天使發出的求救信號所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,coolmint
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以女神的愛作為活動能源的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是接受了大量女神的愛的螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以支撐天使的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你將了一軍 片翼天使凜德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有兩體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在天界也很少有人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙天使凜德的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料 這傢伙不能同時襲擊兩體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 你們貌似打錯王牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你們看看什麼叫真正的王牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 詩寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓…蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要盡全力救出蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸的 我不是以往那個只靠別人幫忙的自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能離開這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判定沒必要保護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們去救助天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依附在蓓兒丹蒂身上的使魔的力量就很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是散發的魔氣不盡三人之力能支撐住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 希兒德說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肩膀上的是行動不能時使用的加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才使用了一次 還有五次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次全部用掉的話 至少能撐過救助時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是對身體非常不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 又不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能無法再次戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 暫時要你們兩個來支撐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 凜德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子已經沒有威脅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔氣停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到使魔會被天使化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一級神蓓兒丹蒂的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 竟讓我興奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想擁有這力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cool and iceblade（寒冰刃）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能運用這力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜打偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 凜德 接下來是你的天使了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 要取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何她的微笑如此給我勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼容易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一 我請求取回coolmint
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,coolmint
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是原來的寄主好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 這是你把一切都獻給天使的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,coolmint告訴我了 你完全信任她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來女神們和比這大好幾倍的喪失感在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你取回了天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你攻擊小貓咪也無法不傷害到天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害？不會傷及一絲毫毛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Valkyrie之名起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想看穿再想躲開的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是傳說中象徵真正力量的黃金之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 雖然不情願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿出50%的認真勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當頭澆我一盆冷水還真要好好獎勵你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 下面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嫌麻煩快逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是希兒德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連逃跑的借口都那麼有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天使食回到它原來的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經無法制止它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的方法就是在此打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們還打不開傳送魔族的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然天使化了 但這孩子是使魔的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德 你來傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然還會襲擊天使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能又會出現犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保證不重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德 你真善良
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算在戰鬥中獲得快感\N但也絕非為了快感而去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為戰鬥而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將戰鬥義務化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不用獨自背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要戰鬥之時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在既然能送它回去 我就想送它回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與黑色之翼共同出現的虛幻之物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身懷兇猛之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持純潔之牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你專心傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門好像不能完全打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 那麼一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜德 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧  sparemint
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓你們見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,coolmint
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sparemint
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不乾脆的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兀兒德的錘子太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那刺不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來 是這樣娛樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不能動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透不過氣來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才起就有柔軟的東西在臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔軟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是他們的娛樂方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這次還破壞得真徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這就是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有你 也無法讓她們見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然能如此運用coolmint
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你真心需要力量 還有充分的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你教會了我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們也很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想著讓她們見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以為自己的力量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以為兩人是一體的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但需要的並不是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是真正需要她們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味追求力量 走了不少歧路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量拯救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 我並沒覺得沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這一路上的經歷全都是我的收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂就是喜歡這樣的螢一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有點羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你當成生涯的友人可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次休假我會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 凜德是絕對會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想見她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然很歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是生涯的友人嘛
